696
00:41:26,851 --> 00:41:30,048
In truth, aren't you all just after my fortune?

697
00:41:30,254 --> 00:41:31,949
Just to see how much longer I have left to live?

698
00:41:32,823 --> 00:41:34,017
Let me tell you something...

699
00:41:34,225 --> 00:41:36,489
I’m going to take my entire fortune with me to...

700
00:41:36,694 --> 00:41:37,956
You don't need to say another word.

701
00:41:38,295 --> 00:41:39,956
I couldn't tell you how many times I've heard that already.

702
00:41:40,231 --> 00:41:42,665
Come on, let's go to the yacht—it'll be fun!

703
00:41:42,867 --> 00:41:44,391
Alright...

704
00:41:46,070 --> 00:41:51,133
Hey, Yulan—I need to talk to you. Yulan!

705
00:41:57,414 --> 00:41:57,709
Do you remember...

706
00:41:57,915 --> 00:41:59,246
...the song that girl sang last time? 707
00:41:59,783 --> 00:42:02,877
Remember? That song was for the girl who brings happiness.

708
00:42:03,087 --> 00:42:03,610
Right? 709
00:42:03,821 --> 00:42:04,480
Oh, right.

710
00:42:05,723 --> 00:42:09,682
I am a little girl, dedicated to giving the gift of happiness,

711
00:42:09,894 --> 00:42:14,024
Scattering it throughout the humble, clustered cottages.

712
00:42:14,231 --> 00:42:18,395
As long as you are willing to strive—to work hard and diligently—

713
00:42:18,602 --> 00:42:23,005
You will naturally discover true happiness.

714
00:42:23,874 --> 00:42:27,742
Do not envy those whose wealth rivals that of nations;

715
00:42:27,945 --> 00:42:31,847
In truth, their hearts are often filled with loneliness.

716
00:42:32,049 --> 00:42:36,179
Life is like a flowing stream;

717
00:42:36,387 --> 00:42:39,914
At its bottom lie the shells of happiness.

718
00:42:40,190 --> 00:42:43,921
If you search carefully and feel around with patience,

719
00:42:44,128 --> 00:42:48,030
And if you find one, you will never be lonely again.

720
00:42:48,232 --> 00:42:52,328
I am a little girl, here to create happiness for others.

721
00:42:52,536 --> 00:42:56,905
Even if I appear to suffer on the surface, my heart remains at peace.

722
00:43:02,746 --> 00:43:07,740
I am a little girl, dedicated to giving the gift of happiness.

723
00:43:07,952 --> 00:43:13,049
I scatter it throughout the crowded little cottages.

724
00:43:13,257 --> 00:43:18,092
As long as you are willing to strive—to work hard and diligently—

725
00:43:18,295 --> 00:43:23,232
You will surely discover true happiness for yourself.

726
00:43:23,767 --> 00:43:27,760
Do not envy those whose wealth rivals that of a nation;

727
00:43:27,972 --> 00:43:32,102
In truth, their hearts are often filled with loneliness.

728
00:43:32,309 --> 00:43:36,336
Life is like a flowing little river;

729
00:43:36,547 --> 00:43:40,540
At the riverbed lie the seashells of happiness.

730
00:43:41,051 --> 00:43:42,712
Wouldn't it be wonderful if we could form a song and dance troupe?

731
00:43:44,121 --> 00:43:45,588
Hey! We can all compose music, after all! 732
00:43:45,789 --> 00:43:47,017
I'll take charge of the choreography.

733
00:43:47,491 --> 00:43:49,049
But the most important thing is still the funding.

734
00:43:49,727 --> 00:43:50,625
How about this miser?

735
00:43:51,727 --> 00:43:52,825
Finally i can rip ass in piece *fart*
